      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without that dealership hassle, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
