    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is an uncompromising example of Stuttgart engineering, preserved in showroom condition. The 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six delivers a linear power band, benefiting from a recent bore scoping and a clean bill of health. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory short-shift kit, the drivetrain provides tactile engagement. The chassis features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and remains taut, with all bushings and mounts showing zero degradation. Finished in a depth-correct Arctic Silver over a flawless black leather interior with no bolster wear, this vehicle retains its original VIN-matching panels and a pristine underbody. Performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, ensuring fade-free deceleration. This is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
